was killed by two Sikh bodyguards. The Hindus were sentenced after
they were convicted of killing four Sikhs in the rioting, the United
News of India news agency said.
   Sikh radicals campaigning for a separate homeland have demanded
punishment of the rioters. Sikhs, who make up 2 percent of India's
population, claim the country's Hindu majority discriminates against
them.
