<DOCNO> AP881026-0137 </DOCNO>
<FILEID>AP-NR-10-26-88 1355EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>r i AM-Ruby-Relatives     10-26 0314</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Ruby-Relatives,0322</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Survivors Report Panic on Sinking Ship</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Ruby Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By EILEEN GUERRERO</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>MANILA, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Typhoon winds howled epeal' Reagan Tax Cuts
