<HEAD>North Korea Angry at Hungary for Seeking Ties with South</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   North Korea gave Hungary a harsh warning Wednesday
over its long-time ally's recent move to establish relations with
South Korea.
   ``If the Hungarian authorities, defying our repeated advice,
persistently choose to deepen their relations with (South Korea),
they will have to bear full responsibility for all the
consequences,'' the North Korean Foreign Ministry said a statement
